394
00:21:41,460 --> 00:21:42,910
I'm so ashamed!

395
00:21:43,880 --> 00:21:44,730
Get up!

396
00:21:45,920 --> 00:21:46,850
Fine.

397
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:48,960
Pull yourself together,

398
00:21:49,030 --> 00:21:50,550
