399
00:21:50,550 --> 00:21:51,550
Fully armed!

400
00:21:51,550 --> 00:21:52,920
Run ten more laps for me!

401
00:21:53,400 --> 00:21:54,240
Hold on tight!

402
00:21:55,310 --> 00:21:56,200
Go quickly!

403
00:21:58,750 --> 00:22:00,150
What are you waiting for?

404
00:22:04,440 --> 00:22:05,440
Faster!

405
00:22:12,920 --> 00:22:14,070
Run faster!

406
00:22:18,830 --> 00:22:20,680
Why so slow? Hurry up!

407
00:22:42,920 --> 00:22:43,960
You fool.

408
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:45,350
Get up!

409
00:22:45,750 --> 00:22:46,670
Get up now!

410
00:22:52,570 --> 00:22:53,530
Get up!

411
00:23:35,920 --> 00:23:36,780
Check, please.

412
00:23:37,640 --> 00:23:38,510
Sir,

413
00:23:38,600 --> 00:23:40,670
someone has already paid your bill.

414
00:23:55,190 --> 00:23:55,920
Come on.

415
00:23:59,460 --> 00:24:01,220
Sit down. Come here.

416
00:24:02,910 --> 00:24:03,460
Sit.

417
00:24:07,370 --> 00:24:08,790
Still thinking about that?

418
00:24:08,790 --> 00:24:10,260
Let it go; it's all in the past.

419
00:24:10,260 --> 00:24:10,970
Oh, yeah.

420
00:24:13,430 --> 00:24:15,080
Maichen, this is for you.

421
00:24:15,170 --> 00:24:15,930
Keep it.

422
00:24:16,550 --> 00:24:18,210
No, Tufang, I can't take that.

423
00:24:18,360 --> 00:24:19,120
Keep it.

424
00:24:19,690 --> 00:24:20,550
Tufang, you...

425
00:24:20,650 --> 00:24:22,540
