00:24:58,440 --> 00:24:59,270
Let's go.

437
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:00,160
Hurry up.

438
00:25:00,180 --> 00:25:01,310
Renjun, I...

439
00:25:07,280 --> 00:25:08,030
What have you been saying

440
00:25:08,030 --> 00:25:09,160
to him all this time?

441
00:25:09,790 --> 00:25:11,270
What could I say?

442
00:25:11,730 --> 00:25:13,270
I helped him find a rickshaw

443
00:25:13,350 --> 00:25:15,000
and sent him straight to the Ginza red-light district.

444
00:25:15,000 --> 00:25:15,630
What?

445
00:25:17,530 --> 00:25:18,640
Gu Maichen

446
00:25:18,660 --> 00:25:20,470
comes from a farming family in Tai'an, Shandong.

447
00:25:20,470 --> 00:25:21,960
He's always been insecure,

448
00:25:21,960 --> 00:25:22,920
then he met that

449
00:25:22,920 --> 00:25:23,920
Japanese instructor.

450
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:25,200
It almost made him want to kill.

451
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:27,440
You have to help him regain his confidence.

452
00:25:27,440 --> 00:25:31,240
But that doesn't mean you should send him to the red-light district.

453
00:25:31,270 --> 00:25:32,750
Just listen to me.

454
00:25:33,160 --> 00:25:34,160
It won't go wrong.

455
00:25:44,660 --> 00:25:46,070
Drillmaster Hirata.

456
00:26:00,270 --> 00:26:02,750
Cadet Li Renjun,

457
00:26:03,000 --> 00:26:04,000
you may go now.

458
00:26:04,020 --> 00:26:04,680
Yes.

459
00:26:30,030 --> 00:26:32,310
Cadet Liang Xiang,

460
00:26:34,160 --> 00:26:35,570
you've learned

461
00:26:37,400 --> 00:26:39,310
how to win people over now.

462
00:26:41,070 --> 00:26:44,180
I'm winning people over?

463
00:26:45,360 --> 00:26:46,230
Sir,

464
00:26:46,920 --> 00:26:48,530
I don't understand what you're talking about.

465
00:26:48,530 --> 00:26:50,160
Your actions today

466
00:26:50,220 --> 00:26:51,610
clearly show that

467
00:26:52,530 --> 00:26:55,930
you're openly inciting our country's trainees

468
00:26:56,440 --> 00:26:59,160
to resist the mental re-education

469
00:26:59,180 --> 00:27:01,350
imposed on you by the Empire of Japan.

470
00:27:01,380 --> 00:27:02,640
That's your interpretation,

471
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:03,230
Drillmaster Hirata.

472
00:27:03,230 --> 00:27:04,200
Shut up!

473
00:27:05,260 --> 00:27:07,190
Did I give you permission to speak?

474
00:27:13,730 --> 00:27:17,880
You think you're clever,

475
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:21,680
buying people's loyalty,

476
00:27:22,640 --> 00:27:24,510
forming factions,

477
00:27:25,270 --> 00:27:26,510
and gathering

478
00:27:27,270 --> 00:27:30,000
loyal allies to run things back home.

479
00:27:30,580 --> 00:27:33,930
But first, you must remember,

480
00:27:34,960 --> 00:27:36,290
understand and embody

481
00:27:36,750 --> 00:27:38,990
the true spirit of the Empire of Japan.

482
00:27:40,830 --> 00:27:42,920
Otherwise, you'll never truly

483
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:45,790
graduate from here.

484
00:27:47,030 --> 00:27:49,310
If that's the case,

485
00:27:57,000 --> 00:27:59,160
then your studies here

486
00:27:59,510 --> 00:28:02,640
will be meaningless.

487
00:28:04,590 --> 00:28:08,270
It's not only a tragedy for your personal education,

488
00:28:09,590 --> 00:28:12,950
but also a failure on my part as your teacher.

489
00:28:27,790 --> 00:28:28,750
Hirata!

490
00:28:30,640 --> 00:28:32,240
Maichen, what are you doing?

491
00:28:32,330 --> 00:28:35,690
I'm going to shoot this arrogant bastard!

492
00:28:39,700 --> 00:28:40,830
Still hiding?

493
00:28:40,850 --> 00:28:42,490
I'll kill you!

494
00:28:42,520 --> 00:28:43,070
Maichen!

495
00:28:43,800 --> 00:28:45,400
Maichen, you've gone crazy!

496
00:28:48,550 --> 00:28:50,270
I'll kill you!

497
00:28:50,320 --> 00:28:53,160
Maichen, stop it!

498
00:28:56,510 --> 00:28:57,510
Stop! Maichen!

499
00:28:58,110 --> 00:28:58,640
Maichen!

500
00:28:59,190 --> 00:29:00,190
I...

501
00:29:01,590 --> 00:29:02,550
Hirata!

502
00:29:12,530 --> 00:29:13,880
I'll kill you!

503
00:29:15,680 --> 00:29:16,920
Hirata!

504
00:29:21,720 --> 00:29:24,310
I'll finish you off, Hirata!

505
00:29:25,030 --> 00:29:26,960
Send him to the military tribunal.

506
00:29:47,180 --> 00:29:48,250
Sir,

507
00:29:48,400 --> 00:29:51,030
Cadet Liang Xiang has arrived as ordered.

508
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:52,310
Come in.

509
00:30:04,550 --> 00:30:06,080
