510
00:30:11,110 --> 00:30:13,310
Thank you for your concern, sir.

511
00:30:13,680 --> 00:30:14,880
It's already healed.

512
00:30:20,320 --> 00:30:21,920
I regret to inform you that

513
00:30:22,680 --> 00:30:23,940
the school has decided

514
00:30:24,030 --> 00:30:26,920
to expel Cadet Gu Maichen.

515
00:30:27,810 --> 00:30:30,400
Despite my best efforts,

516
00:30:31,100 --> 00:30:33,780
I was powerless to stop it.

517
00:30:40,710 --> 00:30:43,430
There were 52 cadets from your country.

518
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:46,090
Now, there are only 51.

519
00:30:47,270 --> 00:30:48,670
By the time you graduate,

520
00:30:48,680 --> 00:30:51,210
I'm not sure if that number will stay the same.

521
00:30:57,100 --> 00:30:58,190
From what I know,

522
00:30:58,350 --> 00:31:00,480
many of you have your own connections.

523
00:31:01,560 --> 00:31:02,840
That Yang Kaizhi

524
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:05,400
is one of them.

525
00:31:06,440 --> 00:31:07,240
Kaizhi?

526
00:31:07,950 --> 00:31:09,080
Why bring him up?

527
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:12,790
Aren't you recruiting military talent?

528
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:15,550
He's one of your targets too, isn't he?

529
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:19,640
I don't know what you're talking about.

530
00:31:22,240 --> 00:31:25,440
Maybe you're right.

531
00:31:27,070 --> 00:31:28,070
What's the saying

532
00:31:29,030 --> 00:31:31,000
from your country?

533
00:31:34,300 --> 00:31:37,100
A fence needs three stakes;

534
00:31:37,770 --> 00:31:39,160
a hero needs

535
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:41,510
three helpers.

536
00:31:45,720 --> 00:31:46,780
You may go now,

537
00:31:46,930 --> 00:31:48,210
Cadet Liang Xiang.

538
00:31:50,190 --> 00:31:51,870
Yes, sir.

539
00:31:55,310 --> 00:31:56,310
By the way,

540
00:31:58,510 --> 00:31:59,670
Miss Yoshiko

541
00:32:00,590 --> 00:32:02,030
asked me to let you know:

542
00:32:02,330 --> 00:32:03,370
Her teacher,

543
00:32:03,830 --> 00:32:05,920
Miss Utako Shimoda, the principal of

544
00:32:06,830 --> 00:32:08,830
Tokyo Jissen Women's University,

545
00:32:09,810 --> 00:32:12,520
