551
00:32:22,650 --> 00:32:25,450
I need to look up some military history materials.

552
00:32:26,680 --> 00:32:27,590
Is that so?

553
00:32:29,410 --> 00:32:31,010
I'll pass the message to her.

554
00:32:42,030 --> 00:32:48,840
[Tokyo Jissen Women's University]

555
00:32:48,300 --> 00:32:49,230
Watch your step.

556
00:32:57,640 --> 00:33:00,270
This is the school motto established

557
00:33:00,590 --> 00:33:03,720
by Principal Utako Shimoda when the school was founded.

558
00:33:04,200 --> 00:33:05,030
By the way,

559
00:33:05,520 --> 00:33:08,920
there will be a tea gathering hosted by the principal this afternoon.

560
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:09,910
The principal

561
00:33:09,930 --> 00:33:14,820
has long been engaged in educating courtly noblewomen,

562
00:33:15,440 --> 00:33:16,880
so most of the students here

563
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:19,290
come from aristocratic families in Tokyo.

564
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:22,350
Today is Sunday.

565
00:33:22,490 --> 00:33:24,860
Everyone's gone home for now.

566
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:27,360
Be back at school before 8 p.m. tonight.

567
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:31,030
Why don't you take some time to settle in first?

568
00:33:33,680 --> 00:33:36,160
You're Shuhong, right?

569
00:33:37,960 --> 00:33:41,440
Take this time to get used to the place.

570
00:33:41,720 --> 00:33:44,330
Tomorrow, Principal Utako Shimoda

571
00:33:44,440 --> 00:33:47,030
