Your outfit

583
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:56,480
must've cost at least

584
00:34:56,480 --> 00:34:57,070
50 yen.

585
00:34:57,090 --> 00:34:58,620
I've only got five minutes.

586
00:34:58,880 --> 00:35:00,070
Don't be so heartless.

587
00:35:00,070 --> 00:35:00,730
Seriously.

588
00:35:00,730 --> 00:35:01,790
What's the matter?

589
00:35:05,790 --> 00:35:06,940
Can't afford the rent,

590
00:35:06,940 --> 00:35:08,040
or can't buy a loaf of bread?

591
00:35:08,040 --> 00:35:09,370
You really know me best.

592
00:35:10,500 --> 00:35:12,160
Just tell me how much you want.

593
00:35:12,850 --> 00:35:13,850
Here's the thing:

594
00:35:14,350 --> 00:35:15,520
I came to Tokyo this time

595
00:35:15,520 --> 00:35:17,320
because I needed to meet some people.

596
00:35:17,320 --> 00:35:17,900
But to meet them,

597
00:35:17,900 --> 00:35:19,280
I have to be in the right places.

598
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:20,110
The problem is,

599
00:35:20,110 --> 00:35:21,940
those places in Tokyo are way too expensive.

600
00:35:21,940 --> 00:35:23,270
Alright, stop nagging.

601
00:35:26,740 --> 00:35:27,600
Is that enough?

602
00:35:27,710 --> 00:35:28,660
Listen,

603
00:35:28,950 --> 00:35:29,750
spend wisely.

604
00:35:29,770 --> 00:35:30,530
I don't have any left either.

605
00:35:30,530 --> 00:35:31,340
Got it.

606
00:35:31,630 --> 00:35:32,840
Don't tell your brother-in-law that I was here.

607
00:35:32,840 --> 00:35:33,780
He doesn't know I'm in Tokyo.

608
00:35:33,780 --> 00:35:34,930
I'm not going to snitch on you.

609
00:35:34,930 --> 00:35:35,520
That's it.

610
00:35:35,520 --> 00:35:38,850
Just don't come running to me only when you're short on cash.

611
00:35:57,840 --> 00:35:58,550
Excuse me,

612
00:35:58,550 --> 00:36:01,230
is this booked by Mr. Yang?

613
00:36:01,670 --> 00:36:03,440
A military officer

614
00:36:03,440 --> 00:36:05,880
in uniform booked it yesterday.

615
00:36:07,930 --> 00:36:08,770
That's right.

616
00:36:09,280 --> 00:36:10,760
Yang Kaizhi,

617
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:11,880
what a tightwad.

618
00:36:12,070 --> 00:36:13,440
It's rare to see him loosen his grip.

619
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:14,690
We should make sure he spends plenty.

620
00:36:14,690 --> 00:36:15,360
Sit down.

621
00:36:19,800 --> 00:36:22,460
Actually, I have another appointment tonight.

622
00:36:23,280 --> 00:36:24,070
Please don't tell me

623
00:36:24,070 --> 00:36:26,650
it's with a member of the Japanese royal family again.

624
00:36:26,650 --> 00:36:27,380
Take a guess.

625
00:36:29,880 --> 00:36:30,720
Who is that?

626
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:33,760
Your former boss.

627
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:36,400
My former boss?

628
00:36:37,710 --> 00:36:38,360
Mr. Yuan?

629
00:36:38,720 --> 00:36:39,320
Exactly.

630
00:36:39,630 --> 00:36:40,360
He is the envoy of

631
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:42,490
Yuan Shikai, the Minister of Beiyang.

632
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:48,590
Got it. It's him.

633
00:36:51,280 --> 00:36:53,360
Why did he only invite you and not me?

634
00:36:53,630 --> 00:36:55,110
That's why I don't want to go.

635
00:36:55,110 --> 00:36:56,310
And I can't go either.

636
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:57,510
Do you know why

637
00:36:57,510 --> 00:36:58,840
he's been avoiding you?

638
00:36:59,200 --> 00:36:59,920
Tell me.

639
00:37:01,110 --> 00:37:02,030
He told me

640
00:37:02,670 --> 00:37:05,090
Yuan Shikai had set aside a commander position for me

641
00:37:05,090 --> 00:37:06,960
in the Beiyang New Army's Third Garrison

642
00:37:06,960 --> 00:37:09,360
and wanted me to join him right after graduation.

643
00:37:09,360 --> 00:37:10,320
Oh my god,

644
00:37:11,100 --> 00:37:12,060
a commander!

645
00:37:12,320 --> 00:37:14,030
Starting off as a commander?

646
00:37:15,260 --> 00:37:16,300
Yeah.

647
00:37:18,400 --> 00:37:19,670
That's his style.

648
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:22,510
That's him.

649
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:24,510
Tufang,

650
00:37:25,280 --> 00:37:26,210
you can go for it.

651
00:37:26,430 --> 00:37:27,460
Why not?

652
00:37:28,190 --> 00:37:29,630
If you join the Beiyang New Army,

653
00:37:29,630 --> 00:37:31,740
I, Li Renjun, might get to ride your coattails in the future,

654
00:37:31,740 --> 00:37:32,490
right?

655
00:37:33,880 --> 00:37:36,440
They gave you a command post right off the bat.

656
00:37:37,670 --> 00:37:38,400
Yuan Shikai

657
00:37:38,400 --> 00:37:40,400
is just using me to make a statement,

658
00:37:40,510 --> 00:37:42,000
putting on a show for the court.

659
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:43,150
As a royal relative myself,

660
00:37:43,150 --> 00:37:46,010
there's no way I'd be some puppet official for Yuan.

661
00:37:46,320 --> 00:37:48,280
Impressive, Tufang!

662
00:37:48,360 --> 00:37:50,360
Your spirit really shines through.

663
00:37:50,690 --> 00:37:52,750
You're going to be someone great someday.

664
00:37:52,750 --> 00:37:53,350
Of course.

665
00:38:02,030 --> 00:38:03,280
Let me introduce you all

666
00:38:03,280 --> 00:38:04,280
to my best friend,

667
00:38:04,360 --> 00:38:05,550
Miss Lee Joohee,

668
00:38:05,570 --> 00:38:07,970
daughter of a wealthy Korean businessman.

669
00:38:09,720 --> 00:38:10,640
Kaizhi.

670
00:38:11,230 --> 00:38:13,420
This... is too exaggerated.

671
00:38:14,230 --> 00:38:15,630
No need to make things up.

672
00:38:16,190 --> 00:38:17,920
A wealthy Korean businessman? Seriously?

673
00:38:17,920 --> 00:38:19,070
Come on, we're bros.

674
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:20,510
No need for that!

675
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:22,480
As long as you like her, Kaizhi,

676
00:38:22,480 --> 00:38:23,510
even if she came from

677
00:38:23,510 --> 00:38:24,030
a brothel,

678
00:38:24,030 --> 00:38:25,760
we'd still have to accept her. Right, Tufang?

679
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:27,760
Renjun, what are you talking about?

680
00:38:28,970 --> 00:38:29,940
Nice to meet you.

681
00:38:30,030 --> 00:38:32,290
I appreciate your guidance and support.

682
00:38:34,960 --> 00:38:35,730
These are the classmates

683
00:38:35,730 --> 00:38:36,930
I mentioned before.

684
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:41,760
You're Liang Xiang.

685
00:38:42,190 --> 00:38:44,320
I was late

686
00:38:44,840 --> 00:38:46,590
that day at the Tokyo Imperial University.

687
00:38:46,590 --> 00:38:48,590
We should have met a year ago.

688
00:38:48,590 --> 00:38:49,800
What a pity.

689
00:38:50,990 --> 00:38:51,870
Kaizhi.

690
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:54,870
Really, Liang Xiang.

691
00:38:55,630 --> 00:38:57,280
She was originally introduced to you,

692
00:38:57,280 --> 00:38:58,540
but you ran away early.

693
00:38:59,280 --> 00:39:01,140
What did you two do behind my back?

694
00:39:01,400 --> 00:39:02,190
Nothing.

695
00:39:02,510 --> 00:39:03,840
Our dear classmate here

696
00:39:04,070 --> 00:39:05,530
is quite the charmer, huh?

697
00:39:07,150 --> 00:39:09,280
I don't know what's going on between you two.

698
00:39:09,280 --> 00:39:09,960
Kaizhi,

699
00:39:10,280 --> 00:39:12,480
since your friend is visiting,

700
00:39:12,510 --> 00:39:13,800
tonight's got to be special.

701
00:39:13,800 --> 00:39:15,150
Let's do it properly.

702
00:39:15,280 --> 00:39:16,190
Bring out the food!

703
00:39:16,190 --> 00:39:17,520
The host is not here yet.

704
00:39:17,760 --> 00:39:19,360
We'll serve the dishes when he arrives.

705
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:19,840
Fine.

706
00:39:20,550 --> 00:39:22,550
Kaizhi, you're always getting others to pay up.

707
00:39:22,550 --> 00:39:23,320
When's it our turn

708
00:39:23,320 --> 00:39:24,760
to spend your money, huh?

709
00:39:25,480 --> 00:39:26,920
Now that you've got ties with a Korean tycoon,

710
00:39:26,920 --> 00:39:30,120
you'd better not embarrass the dignity of the Great Qing!

711
00:39:34,920 --> 00:39:35,880
I'm late.

712
00:39:36,030 --> 00:39:36,880
Sorry.

713
00:39:37,440 --> 00:39:38,840
Let me introduce you all.

714
00:39:39,000 --> 00:39:40,840
This is my cousin, Yang Yifan.

715
00:39:41,030 --> 00:39:42,630
His courtesy name is Hanhua.

716
00:39:54,870 --> 00:39:56,330
They're in a private room.

717
00:39:56,800 --> 00:39:57,880
Keep an eye on them.

718
00:39:57,900 --> 00:39:59,130
Yes, sir.
